title: Bella Hadid amazing painted on dress 👗🤯

media:group.media:title: Bella Hadid amazing painted on dress 👗🤯
media:group.media:description: Coperni’s spring 2023 show dedicated its runway to “women of this world.” Bella Hadid takes center stage as the main event. Three men spray painted a dress onto her body. The dress was completed by another artist who used her hands and a pair of scissors to sculpt Bella’s dress.
